607
01:08:06,339 --> 01:08:12,140
of people in America and across the world."

608
01:08:12,140 --> 01:08:19,920
The speech had been announced two months earlier,
and King knew how important it would be. It

609
01:08:19,920 --> 01:08:28,089
would only be five minutes long, so he had
to be very careful in choosing his words.

610
01:08:28,089 --> 01:08:32,800
