617
01:09:12,880 --> 01:09:18,790
This chapter looks at the question of when
to take original action. I'll discuss how

618
01:09:18,790 --> 01:09:27,190
delaying can be useful, and why procrastinating
can be a good thing. I'll look at how entrepreneurs

619
01:09:27,190 --> 01:09:33,670
who are first to market with a product can
have difficulties; why older innovators are

620
01:09:33,670 --> 01:09:40,720
