670
01:15:12,100 --> 01:15:20,020
While he was speaking, the singer Mahalia
Jackson was behind him. She shouted, "Tell

671
01:15:20,020 --> 01:15:28,610
them about the dream, Martin." He continued
with his speech, but she shouted it again.

672
01:15:28,610 --> 01:15:36,280
In front of a crowd of 250,000, with millions
more watching on television, King pushed his

673
01:15:36,280 --> 01:15:42,240
notes to one side and talked about his dream.

674
01:15:42,240 --> 01:15:48,350
According to Drew Hansen in his book, The
Dream, King was still cutting out lines and

675
01:15:48,350 --> 01:15:55,150
